{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I would say by-- by 19-- by-- by September, October 1942 when the last transports left Vienna, 90% of the Jews, 95% of the Jews were-- were-- there were about 300,000 Jews in Austria, of which 200-- approximately-- I don't-- approximately 200,000 were in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In 1938, all the Jews from all over Austria had to come to Vienna, and they-- they started to send them out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And by the end of-- by-- or September, October 1942, 95% of what was left was-- you know, what had not been able to get out in '38 and '39 when immigration, if you had somebody or some special case, was possible.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One of my father's sister got out and went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the rest of us, we didn't have any relatives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nobody from our family had ever emigrated to any place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had a good life at home, so we didn't have anybody outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So we had paid landing money for a permit to Australia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were supposed to leave sometimes in-- in-- in-- in-- was it like-- in October, the 8th or the 10th of October 1939.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then the war came before this, so there was no way of getting out of Austria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My father had had some money that was not in Austria in a bank.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was in a bank in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was able to pay, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was not much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was about 100, 150 English pounds a head so that they would let you in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had-- we were supposed to go to Melbourne in Australia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Well, of course, the war started in-- in-- in September of-- September '39.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So we never got out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
